    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo serves as the base requirements for Authorization of Internet Resources and Services (AIRS).  It presents an architectural framework for understanding the authorization of Internet resources and services and derives requirements for authorization protocols.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
